Return values
The function returns a promise that resolves to an object with an array of Event IDs that were sent. These events can be used to look up the event in the Inngest dashboard or via
[the REST API](https://api-docs.inngest.com/docs/inngest-api/pswkqb7u3obet-get-an-event)
